Class AbstractShortBigList

    • java.util.AbstractCollection<java.lang.Short>
      • it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.shorts.AbstractShortCollection

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BigList<java.lang.Short>, ShortBigList, ShortCollection, ShortIterable, ShortStack, Size64, Stack<java.lang.Short>, java.lang.Comparable<BigList<? extends java.lang.Short>>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Short>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Short>

    AbstractShortBigList.ShortSubList, ShortBigArrayBigList, ShortBigLists.ListBigList, ShortBigLists.Singleton

    public abstract class AbstractShortBigList
extends AbstractShortCollection
implements ShortBigList, ShortStack
    An abstract class providing basic methods for big lists implementing a type-specific big list interface.
